sonobus (1.4.2-1) buster; urgency=medium

  * Added Auto Jitter buffer adjust drop rate threshold option
  * Prevent user leave/join messages in chat in public groups
  * Simplified update check download
  * Fixed layout of public group page
  * Updated some visual elements (time sliders, etc)
  * Updated translations

 --  Kevin Doren <kevin@doren.org>  Thu, 25 Mar 2021 20:50:00 -0800

sonobus (1.4.0-2) buster; urgency=medium

  * Fix bug in build install script which packaged in correct binary
  * Add symlink to old name for script compatibility.

 --  Kevin Doren <kevin@doren.org>  Wed, 24 Mar 2021 01:10:00 -0800

sonobus (1.4.0-1) buster; urgency=medium

  * Multi-channel (>2) support added
  * Input Mixer added to control how the inputs are mixed and grouped
  * Input effects are now per channel as configured by grouping
  * Full gate/compressor/eq effects now available per user track
  * You can route remote users to specific outputs
  * Can now insert Audio Unit plugin in "instrument" slots
  * Added minimal/full view mode choice
  * Recording filenames now include group name
  * Added support for MP3 playing on platforms that didn't have it
  * Initially mute incoming audio of new connections
  * Added Default User Volume level in options
  * Text Chat added
  * Self-monitoring delay (and backing track delay) options
  * Added Group Latency Match feature
  * Added command line options to start sonobus and connect
  * Initial translation support for several languages
  * Many bugfixes

 --  Kevin Doren <kevin@doren.org>  Tue, 23 Mar 2021 00:20:00 -0800

